Compilation of all Security related tasks
-----------------------------------------
Title: Password blackout so actual characters are not visible.

Description:

  Blackout/star out password characters as user enters them so the actual characters of password
  are not visible.

Related scenario(s):

  - Security Scenario - Scenario 1: Password Blackout.

Time estimate(s):

  ~30 mins

