Title: Enforce Strong Password format for increased security.

Description:

  Enforce a strong password format such as 8-16 chars, one capital letter,
  and at least one number or special character. This will provide increased security.

Related scenario(s):

  - Security Scenario - Scenario 2: Enforce Strong Password.

Time estimate(s):

