Title: Two-Factor Authentication.

Description:

  Allow two-factor authentication for improved security. For example, user enters correct password for
  their account and then needs to enter 4 digit PIN from an email sent by BlueBank to log in to their account.

Related scenario(s):

  - Security Scenario - Scenario 6: Two-Factor Authentication.

Time estimate(s):

